  }, "v5"), mdx("p", null, "nh\u01B0ng ta c\xF3 m\u1ED9t chi\xEAm bao khi\u1EBFn ta hoang mang. Trong khi ta \u0111ang n\u1EB1m tr\xEAn gi\u01B0\u1EDDng, ta th\u1EA5y nh\u1EEFng h\xECnh \u1EA3nh v\xE0 d\u1ECB t\u01B0\u1EE3ng trong tr\xED ta l\xE0m ta kinh ho\u1EA3ng. "), mdx("h6", {
