  }, "v8"), mdx("p", null, "Sau c\xF9ng c\xF3 \u0110a-ni\xEAn \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EB7p ta. Ta g\u1ECDi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi l\xE0 B\xEAn-t\u01A1-s\xE1t-xa \u0111\u1EC3 t\u1ECF l\xF2ng t\xF4n k\xEDnh c\xE1c th\u1EA7n c\u1EE7a ta v\xEC linh c\u1EE7a c\xE1c th\xE1nh th\u1EA7n \u1EDF trong ng\u01B0\u1EDDi. Ta thu\u1EADt cho ng\u01B0\u1EDDi nghe \u0111i\u1EC1m chi\xEAm bao ta. "), mdx("h6", {
